}

### ============================================
### USER - Perfil y Actualización
### ============================================

### Obtener mi información (Me)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Completar perfil (tras login Google)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "userType": "PARTICULAR",
  "surname": "Mora Perez",
  "dniNif": "87654321X",
  "address": "Calle Nueva 5",
  "population": "Valencia",
  "province": "Valencia",
  "phone": "655443322",
  "paymentMethod": "Tarjeta",
  "bank": "Caixa",
  "bicSwift": "CAIXESMM",
  "iban": "ES2100001111222233334444"
}

